I think this can be more than zendesk because just noticed there is another GraphQL query that probably leads to shop info disclosure. **I cannot investigate it anymore because the site is down**: 

```
"
  query getShopInfo($domain: String) {
    shop(myshopifyDomain: $domain) {
      shopInfo {
        errors {
          code
          message
        }
        id
        domain
        myshopifyDomain
        currency
        countryName
        createdAt
        planDisplayName
        planName
        planPeriod
        timezone
        users {
          id
          firstName
          lastName
          email
          userType
          permissions
        }
      }
      reportify(since: 12) {
        gmv
      }
      askPrompts {
        edges {
          node {
            name
            url
            zendeskTag
            openOpportunity
            eligible
          }
        }
      }
    }
  }

```

I am assuming this can result in more disclosure such as email, name and other information about the user.

Thanks! Please let me know if I can be of any help :) 
Cheers!
